The optimization introduces a semantic change that breaks the algorithm. The broadcast dimensions mapping expects elements at specific indices corresponding to the original dimension ordering.

**Verdict**: This is not a valid optimization because it changes the behavior of the algorithm. The vector elements end up in reverse order compared to what the subsequent code expects.